Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is excited to offer, for lease, 120 Northcorp Boulevard, Broadmeadows. This substantial purpose-built distribution centre is strategically located 17km* north of Melbourne’s CBD and offers potential occupiers the ability to lease areas ranging from 6,000 – 60,000sqm*. 

Positioned in the heart of Melbourne's North, 120 Northcorp Boulevard is well connected via a number of major road arterials including the Metropolitan Ring Road, Hume Freeway, Hume Highway & Tullamarine Freeway. The impending North-East Link project will further cement the location as a serious consideration for major transport & logistics occupiers

120 Northcorp Boulevard, Broadmeadows offers the following features;

+ Total Gross Lettable Area (GLA): 60,044sqm*
+ Site Area: 250,000sqm*
+ Areas available ranging from 6,000 – 60,000sqm*
+ 21 b-double finger docks & 40 recessed loading docks
+ Existing automation with the ability to be re-purposed for a variety of uses 
+ Low site coverage offering expansion opportunity & drive around capability
+ 344 on-site car spaces
+ Large hardstand areas for ideal truck maneuverability and parking
+ High power supply
+ Site allowing for 24/7 operation

For further information regarding this landmark leasing opportunity, please contact the exclusive marketing agents, CBRE.

*approx
